previous: U-T San Diego is a daily newspaper published in San Diego, California. It was renamed in 2012 from The San Diego Union-Tribune, a 1992 merger between San Diego Union and San Diego Evening Tribune. The San Diego Sun merged with the Evening Tribune in 1939. In 2012, the competitor North County Times newspaper was merged into U-T San Diego.
